cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.SI

This paper deals with natural language processing and sentiment analysis, which are closely related to the sub-fields of computational linguistics (cs.CL), machine learning (cs.LG), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of best-worst scaling for annotation also involves statistical methods and data analysis, which are relevant to information retrieval (cs.IR) and social media analysis (cs.SI).
